          -  Subjects scheduled for otorinolaryngoiatric surgery in general anesthesia of at least
             3 hours duration

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI less than 18

          -  BMI greater than 33

          -  Diabetes mellitus requiring medication

          -  Treatment with diuretics

          -  ACE-inhibitors

          -  Angiotensin II antagonists

          -  Cortisone

          -  Lithium

          -  Diseases of the kidney

          -  Females:

               -  Pregnancy

               -  Menopause

               -  Endocrine dysfunction influencing menstruation
      </textblock>
